reviewText: great story, Its on Netflix but I had to have a copy since I am a huge Dunlop fan. M. Dunlop is a true badass and he carries on the epic Dunlop saga.

Works perfectly on my PS4 (which is from 2014).
Awesome documentary about great people. And Liam Neeson is the perfect narrator.
On par with the Faster series.
Great  DVD but won't play on some USA DVD Players.
